nakikita ko.

180
00:14:00.339 --> 00:14:02.457
"Baek Hoon-ah"?

181
00:14:02.508 --> 00:14:05.961
Parang pamilyar ang pangalan.

182
00:14:07.179 --> 00:14:08.406
Hoon-ah?

183
00:14:08.430 --> 00:14:11.076
Hindi ba ikaw ang Nightingale ng Jou-ri?

184
00:14:11.100 --> 00:14:12.202
