grade nung lumipat ka sa Seoul.

188
00:14:23.904 --> 00:14:26.648
- Ikaw ay malamang na 9.
- Tama.

189
00:14:26.907 --> 00:14:30.887
Palagi kang magaling kumanta.

190
00:14:30.911 --> 00:14:32.848
No wonder naging composer ka.

191
