193
00:14:42.798 --> 00:14:45.402
Makakapagpahinga ka na kung tapos ka na niyan.

194
00:14:45.426 --> 00:14:47.544
hindi pa ako tapos.

195
00:14:48.971 --> 00:14:50.964
Kakainin ko rin ang balat.

196
00:14:52.558 --> 00:14:54.217
Okay.

197
00:15:01.734 --> 00:15:04.379
Kung ikaw ay maninirahan sa nayong ito,

198
00:15:04.403 --> 00:15:06.798
mas mabuting huwag makinig sa sinasabi niya.

199
00:15:06.822 --> 00:15:09.134
Halika na. Matagal akong nakatira sa Seoul.

200
00:15:09.158 --> 00:15:12.110
Hindi ko na siya pinapansin.

201
00:15:14.830 --> 00:15:18.518
Anyway, masaya akong makita kang muli.

202
00:15:18.542 --> 00:15:20.770
Nandito ka ba for good?

203
00:15:20.794 --> 00:15:23.413
Well, nakikita mo...

204
00:15:26.133 --> 00:15:27.694
Yong-rak.

205
00:15:27.718 --> 00:15:29.878
Yong-rak.

206
00:15:30.846 --> 00:15:33.992
<i>Kumalat na ang sakit sa paa at bibig
sa buong North at South Jeolla Province,</i>

207
00:15:34.016 --> 00:15:35.869
